{"tid":1772802,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Tom Holland : 我一個電話促使迪士尼Sony和解 蜘蛛俠留喺Marvel","createTime":"2019-12-07T03:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T13:01:27.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5a895dfb069b6c220dec3ee5bb947aef71d65635","tid":1772802,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:24:06.000Z","msg":"今年8月「蜘蛛俠」鬧出版權風波，近年Sony和Marvel取得協議，擁有版權的Sony讓蜘蛛俠進入《復仇者聯盟》，但今年暑假雙方卻因財而鬧翻，一度傳出蜘蛛俠從此退出Marvel宇宙。雖然最近兩方面已重新傾掂數，但原來背後還有故事，飾演「蜘蛛俠」的湯姆賀倫（Tom Holland）亦是一大功臣。<br />\n<br />\n最近他上名嘴Jimmy Kimmel的節目，表示曾致電迪士尼CEO Bob Iger表示：「這5年是我生命中最精采的時光，謝謝你改變我的一生，我希望未來還有機會合作。」Bob更表示這個電話幫助了蜘蛛俠留在Marvel。不過這個故事還有下文，湯姆表示，事後他收到Bob的電郵，指想跟他再通個電話。幾日之後，湯姆與家人去了酒吧，他飲了3大杯啤酒，之後就突然收到電話，湯姆笑指：「我估這是Bob Iger，但我現在醉了！」後來他要強裝清醒，而那個電話也促使了Bob決心與Sony的高層達成共識。現在蜘蛛俠已確認會回歸Marvel，他亦會拍攝第3部蜘蛛俠獨立作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191207/60350013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191207%2F60350013&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=09a14f85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191207%2F60350013&h=2caa3374\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191207/60350013</a>"},{"pid":"953ecfba7d19603c4dda8ae370d8bd8ccabca888","tid":1772802,"uid":28159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"電影界Donald Trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350f978e4a03328d0492a9fd3d044417194a213d","tid":1772802,"uid":97212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"953ecfba7d19603c4dda8ae370d8bd8ccabca888","tid":1772802,"uid":28159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"電影界Donald Trump <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"its just mkting, dude"}]}